   All characters in this software (Asking The Tao) that are based on historical figures (including but not limited to representatives of Confucianism, Mohism, Taoism, Legalism, School of Names, School of Yin-Yang, School of Diplomacy, Eclectics, Agrarianism, and School of Fiction) are artistic interpretations incorporating fictional elements of the "Bronze Mechanism City" worldview and Oriental steampunk aesthetics.

