### Metal Shine
```css
.metal-shine {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.metal-shine::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -50%;
  left: -50%;
  width: 200%;
  height: 200%;
  background: linear-gradient(
    45deg,
    transparent 40%,
    rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 50%,
    transparent 60%
  );
  animation: shine 3s infinite;
}

@keyframes shine {
