🔥 HOT (always loaded):
   memory.md: 0 entries

🌡️ WARM (load on demand):
   projects/: 0 files
   domains/: 0 files

❄️ COLD (archived):
   archive/: 0 files

⚙️ Mode: Passive
```

### 7. Add HEARTBEAT.md Steering

Add this section to your `HEARTBEAT.md`:

```markdown
